<span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">winter </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">contingency plans of the TfL Asset Management</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> Directorate and the </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">           Borough </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">W</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">inter Teams as </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">explained above</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">2.9</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Our </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">London River Services </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">division </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">maintain</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">s</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> stocks of salt to ensure that </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">pedestrian </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">access areas on </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">approaches to </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">its</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> piers are maintained for </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">safe use of passengers. Access roads to the Woolwich Ferry </span><span style="font-family:Arial; fon