1October and 30</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt; vertical-align:super"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">April. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">           </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Treatment</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> plans are maintained by </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">our </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Roads Directorate. These are </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">            </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">reviewed</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> and optimised </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> annually with input from </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">across our organisation </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">as </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">            </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">well as </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">from </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">e</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">xternal stakeholders including b</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">oroughs. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">2.</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">12</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">The winter season started on 1</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> October</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> and as of that date w</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">e are</span><span styl